msgid "**Attachments thread alongside text:** `room.send_attachment` calls carry an `AttachmentConfig::reply(...)` with `EnforceThread::Threaded` when a thread anchor is present, so PDFs / images / voice notes land inside the bot's thread instead of the main timeline."
