#: src/channels/acp.md
msgid "The `cwd` from `session/new` becomes the `SecurityPolicy` workspace boundary used by all file and shell tools for that session. Note: the agent's system prompt currently reflects the daemon's global `workspace_dir` rather than the session `cwd` — this does not affect enforcement, only the directory the model believes it is working in."
