#: src/foundations/fnd-002-documentation-standards.md
msgid "The root `AGENTS.md` is the project's strongest existing contribution to AI-assisted development. It tells AI coding assistants the commands to run, the architecture to respect, the risk tiers to apply, and the anti-patterns to avoid. It works because it is specific, opinionated, and short."
