msgid "`for_agent` reads the parent's `risk_profile` and `[agents.<alias>.workspace.read_memory_from]` to build the inherited allowlist; the parent's own alias is always added so a SubAgent always sees its parent's own memory rows. `build` applies optional narrowing (see [Permission inheritance](#permission-inheritance) below) and returns a validated `SubAgentContext`."
